snippet.title: Last Tide: MEGALODON!
snippet.description:
Available Now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/858590/Last_Tide/

Last Tide is an underwater battle royale. Face ferocious Megalodons, Great Whites and more! Chum-grenade your enemies so sharks attack them! Use unique aquatic equipment, climb the leaderboards, and experience underwater freedom of movement!
